overview:
Sebastian is a highly effective leader in diverse environments including start-up and early stage growth. People oriented and driven for results has built and developed solid teams who learn how to lead.

Head of Marketing at RESULTS.com - The Business Execution Experts and cofounder of Chief Execution Officer, Road2Argentina among some other endeavors.

His purpose is to inspire people to bring their very best to what they are building. His talent is learning and bringing a fresh, innovative and simple approach to whatever they do and Sebastian’s experience is dedicated to supporting game-changing entrepreneurs and business leaders by helping them to execute and grow their businesses.

Experience with multiple cultures, Bi-lingual in English and Spanish has extensive entrepreneurs and business leaders connections all across Argentina, New Zealand and United States.
